      "message": "Ideally, all future board shouldn\u0027t have dpplus support. I\u0027m not too leaning on adding a USE flag that no future board would use. It\u0027s good to have USE flag that would be actively used by future board but not the opposite. WDYT?\n\nI filed crbug.com/1157618 to request negation support for SoftwareDeps.",
